condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :3.02 (b) | Description :Update the Procurement Plan every 12 months | Frequency :Yearly
Finance Agreement :3.04 and 3.05 | Description :The Borrower shall enter into subsidiary loan agreements with the participatingprovinces. Effectiveness condition | Due Date :10-Aug-2011
Finance Agreement :3.04 and 3.05 | Description :The Borrower shall enter into subsidiary loan agreements with the participatingprovinces. Effectiveness condition | Due Date :31-Mar-2006
Finance Agreement :3.06 | Description :The Borrower shall carry out the Project accordance with the provisions of the OperationalManual. Effectiveness condition | Due Date :31-Mar-2006

Finance Agreement :3.09 | Description :The Borrower shall operate and maintain a Project Implementation Unit. ProcurementSpecialist should be hired no later than 2 months after effectiveness | Due Date :15-Nov-2006
Finance Agreement :3.10 | Description :Maintain procedures to monitor progress in project implementation. Reports are to befurnished each calendar semester | Frequency :Quarterly
Finance Agreement :3.11 | Description :The Borrower shall prepare not later than 6 months after effectiveness the baselineindicators for the project | Due Date :16-Mar-2007
Finance Agreement :3.12 | Description :Ensure that any works to be carried out do not involve any Resettlement | Frequency :Yearly
Finance Agreement :3.13 | Description :Create and maintain a specific budget line entry in each of its annual budgets | Frequency:Yearly

Finance Agreement :3.14 | Description :Each Participating Province shall prepare annual road investment programs not later thanDecember 30 of each calendar year and progr ess reports each calendar semester | Frequency :Yearly
Finance Agreement :3.15 | Description :Each Participating Province shall carry out an annual road and traffic survey not later thanDecember 31 of each calendar year | Frequency :Yearly
Finance Agreement :3.16 | Description :The Borrower shall establish a procurement information system not later than six monthsafter the Effective Date | Due Date :15-Mar-2007

Finance Agreement :3.17 | Description :The Borrower shall develop a develop a new financial management information system not laterthan one calendar year after the Effect ive Date | Due Date :14-Sep-2007
Finance Agreement :4.01 | Description :The Borrower shall have financial statements audited | Frequency :Yearly
Finance Agreement :4.02 | Description :The Borrower shall prepare and furnish financial monitoring reports | Frequency :Quarterly
